messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 3/20/2004 2:16:53 PM Mountain Standard Time,
scott-wecht@... writes:
I tried to get there from several routes including google. I get the same
address but no go. Does anyone know if the site is having tech difficulties or
is it just me.
========

If you can see anything at all, scroll down to the bottom and there's a link
to an alternative version. On mine it doesn't show without scrolling down.

If you have two browsers, try a different one.

One of mine brings it up, the other doesn't.

Sandra
